PNSS examples

options(rgl.useNULL = TRUE)
library(rgl)
library(shapes)

Digit3 dataset

n.pc <- 10
plotshapes(digit3.dat[,,4], joinline = 1:13)

out <- pnss3d(digit3.dat, n.pc = n.pc)

round(out$percent, 4)
 [1] 59.1348 13.1621  9.0604  6.7183  3.8537  1.8833  1.6480
 [8]  1.1267  0.7847  0.3394

Female Gorilla dataset

plotshapes(gorf.dat,joinline=c(1,6,7,8,2,3,4,5,1))

out <- pnss3d(gorf.dat, n.pc = n.pc)

round(out$percent, 4)
 [1] 35.8779 22.8999 11.1872  8.7032  5.8607  3.6612  3.4074
 [8]  2.8784  2.0272  1.6282

Male Gorilla dataset

out <- pnss3d(gorm.dat, n.pc = n.pc)

round(out$percent, 4)
